gmoji\" />好呀<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n溝女版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（正！女神呀，好怕醜！為左香港都要博下）唔好意思....可唔可以阻你少少時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: (望一望，點睇都唔似有資格做保險/sale屎）咩事？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 我地有個聯署，想你幫幫香港人...（越講越細聲）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我簽左啦！唉呀你咁閃縮點得架，我陪你一齊問其他人。<br />\n<br />\n幾個鐘後，問左幾千人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 西利啦，講野流利左，無咁怕醜仔！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 唔....唔係架，我見到你我都怕醜架...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 傻佬，我比我電話你，同你訓練下！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a43809ea4567d42d5103960f879b31f61d19a9","tid":2187500,"uid":327010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7212057547afb390105d99773f9bda48fb850c7a","tid":2187500,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifBp26a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifBp26a.jpg&h=d635f1d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40aaef8eb55bd6469f113135b30c1ba5d5291f19","tid":2187500,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7212057547afb390105d99773f9bda48fb850c7a","tid":2187500,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifBp26a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F